_sText:
Terrorists try to bomb ancient temples. 
Bombsite A is located in a desert world, bombsite B is a nordish stone circle.

Every team starts from its own home world via a stargate.
Stargates connect the two worlds (bomspot a/b).

Tip:
Bots have little problems to find the gates.
Do not forget to communicate with them if You want them to come with You to the gates.

Have fun!

BitStreamer
